#: src/kcmplymouth_actions.actions:54
msgctxt "Name"
msgid "Save the Plymouth Theme"
msgstr "प्लायमाउथ विषयं रक्षतु"

#: src/kcmplymouth_actions.actions:103
msgctxt "Description"
msgid "Authenticate to change the boot splash screen."
msgstr "बूट् स्प्लैश स्क्रीन परिवर्तयितुं प्रमाणीकरणं कुर्वन्तु ।"

#: src/kcmplymouth_actions.actions:144
