#: src/kcmplymouth_actions.actions:234
msgctxt "Name"
msgid "Uninstall a new Plymouth Theme"
msgstr "एकं नूतनं Plymouth Theme अनइन्स्टॉल कुर्वन्तु"

#: src/kcmplymouth_actions.actions:283
msgctxt "Description"
msgid "Authenticate to uninstall a Plymouth theme."
msgstr "प्लायमाउथ् विषयवस्तुं विस्थापयितुं प्रमाणीकरणं कुर्वन्तु।"

